## How DevStarter Works Without Claude Code

DevStarter ships 51 workflows and 83 specialist agents. There are no slash
commands outside Claude Code — instead each workflow exposes a **Universal
Prompt**.

To run any workflow:

1. Open the matching skill file in `skills/devstarter-<name>/SKILL.md`
2. Copy the `## 🌐 Universal Prompt` block at the bottom
3. Paste it into your AI tool and follow the gates

Or use the helper script:

```
bash devstarter-invoke.sh <workflow>      # prints the runnable prompt
bash devstarter-invoke.sh menu            # lists all workflows
bash devstarter-invoke.sh change          # e.g. add/fix/remove feature
```

Full setup per AI tool: `docs/multi-ai-guide.md`

