## Workflow Rules (apply to every AI)

- **Stop at every ⛔ GATE** and wait for explicit approval before continuing.
- **Read before acting** — read the relevant `sdlc/devstarter-*.md` runbook
  and `agents/devstarter-*.md` agent spec from this install before producing output.
- **Conventional commits** — `feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`.
- **Branch discipline** — never edit on a protected branch
  ({{VCS_TYPE}} default: main / develop). Work on `feature/*` or `fix/*`.

