## Limitations vs Claude Code

| Capability | Available here |
|------------|----------------|
| All SDLC workflows + agents | ✅ via Universal Prompts |
| Gate-based approvals | ✅ AI stops and waits |
| Slash commands `/devstarter-*` | ❌ Claude Code only |
| Lifecycle hooks / auto-resume | ❌ Claude Code only — track progress manually |
| MCP server integrations | ❌ depends on your AI tool |

